==历史==
2015年11月9日，北马区通勤铁路正式营运并在[[莪仑站|莪仑站]]、[[北海站_(马来西亚)|北海站]]和[[甘文丁站|甘文丁站]]之间的车站提供服务。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.thestar.com.my/News/Nation/2015/08/24/KTM-Utara-waiting-SPAD-ok/ | work = The Star | title = Northern KTM Komuter service pending SPAD approval | date = 24 August 2015 | accessdate = 2017-01-13 | archive-date = 2020-09-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200930035216/https://www.thestar.com.my/News/Nation/2015/08/24/KTM-Utara-waiting-SPAD-ok/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.thestar.com.my/News/Nation/2015/08/25/Commuter-rail-to-service-north-soon/ | work = The Star | title = Commuter rail to service north soon | date = 25 August 2015 | accessdate = 2017-01-13 | archive-date = 2017-09-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170906064330/http://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2015/08/25/commuter-rail-to-service-north-soon/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.thestar.com.my/Videos/2015/09/11/Northern-folks-to-enjoy-new-mode-of-transportation/ | work = The Star | title = Northern folks to enjoy new mode of transportation | date = 11 September 2015 | access-date = 2017-01-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170827085852/http://www.thestar.com.my/videos/2015/09/11/northern-folks-to-enjoy-new-mode-of-transportation/ | archive-date = 2017-08-27 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.thestar.com.my/News/Nation/2015/09/11/KTMB-northern-region-new-service/ | work = The Star | title = KTM Commuter service connecting Kamunting and Gurun launched | date = 11 September 2015 | accessdate = 2017-01-13 | archive-date = 2020-09-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200930042659/https://www.thestar.com.my/News/Nation/2015/09/11/KTMB-northern-region-new-service/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>在2016年1月1日，开始提供从[[北海站_(马来西亚)|北海站]]至[[巴东勿刹站|巴东勿刹站]]的服务，而在当时，[[KTM电动列车服务|KTM电动列车服务]]在此区域的服务也同时被终止。<ref name="ButterworthPdgBesar">{{cite news | url = http://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2016/01/01/ktm-komuter-service-butterworth-padang-besar/ | work = The Star | title = KTM Komuter service from Butterworth to Padang Besar launched | date = 1 January 2016 | accessdate = 2017-01-13 | archive-date = 2020-09-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200930032811/https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2016/01/01/ktm-komuter-service-butterworth-padang-besar/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=PENAMATAN PERKHIDMATAN TREN ETS BUTTERWORTH – PADANG BESAR – BUTTERWORTH EG9501 DAN EG9502, BERMULA 01 JANUARI 2016|url=http://homepage.ktmb.com.my/images/NotisPenamatan.pdf|accessdate=1 January 2016|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160202205710/http://homepage.ktmb.com.my/images/NotisPenamatan.pdf|archivedate=2016年2月2日}}</ref>

在2016年1月17日，莪仑－北海－甘文丁线被拆分为两条线路，分别为北海－莪仑和北海－甘文丁。这两条线路后来在2016年9月1日被改良为'''巴东勿刹线'''和'''硝山线'''。<ref>{{cite web|title=Penambahbaikan Perkhidmatan Tren Shuttle KTM Komuter di Sektor Utara|url=http://homepage.ktmb.com.my/images/14012016SIARANMEDIAKOMUTERSEKTORUTARA.pdf|accessdate=28 January 2016|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160202203453/http://homepage.ktmb.com.my/images/14012016SIARANMEDIAKOMUTERSEKTORUTARA.pdf|archivedate=2016年2月2日}}</ref>

